<span id="freeTextContainer16339808252642277757">I LOVE THIS BOOK! I read it almost annually.<br/><br/>My husband was a fire fighter for the Forest Service, but not a smokejumper, which is why we originally purchased the book. However, I fell in love with this tale that covers a tragedy in almost classic epic style, combined with the mystery story of the science of how this event happened.</span>

